TI  - Teacher Candidates’ Perception of Their First Week School Placement: Comparison between Online and Face-To-Face Practicum Learnings and Challenges
PY  - 2022
T2  - Perspektivy Nauki i Obrazovania
VL  - 60
IS  - 6
SP  - 598
EP  - 611
